title: Live updates: Miami Hurricanes at Florida State Seminoles
text:
October 10, 2015 Live updates: Miami Hurricanes at Florida State Seminoles 
UM takes on FSU at Doak Campbell Stadium in Tallahassee at 8:00 p.m. on Saturday, Oct. 10 
Miami Herald sportswriters Susan Miller Degnan and Manny Navarro provide live updates Fans show their support as the University of Miami team arrives at Doak Campbell Stadium for the game against Florida State University in Tallahassee on Saturday, October 10, 2015. AL DIAZ adiaz@miamiherald.com i
